OL,7,FMore than 30 million tourists flock
OL,8,Fto Greece and its islands each year,
OL,9,Fand most head for the beach. But for
OL,10,Fwheelchair-bound people, simple
OL,11,Fpleasures such as going for a dip can
OL,12,Fbe virtually impossible unless a lot
OL,13,Fof help is at hand.
OL,15,F"Swimming in the sea is a dream for
OL,16,Fmost of us," says Linda Zervakis, a
OL,17,FGreek woman who has multiple
OL,18,Fsclerosis.
OL,3,CThe solar-powered tech helping those
OL,4,Cwith mobility issues to hit the beach
OL,5,Cacross Greece
